sn't raunchy, dirty mouthed and yet lifts up women and encourages them to take charge of their lives with positive steps. Thanks Kaira, I am so looking forward to your next book! Can I make a suggestion? How about Book 2 be about Katherine and Mel and how they take the reigns back to their lives?\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eThis book is for adults. Teens won't have any understanding of the crises in Kelly's life and also her friends - but then again they would understand what Mel (the anorexic teen) is feeling and would sympathize with her feelings and situation. There are discussion questions at the end of the book and it is an ideal book for a book club.","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4098342?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/172386615"},"likeCount":2,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":0,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Work:kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.rCxHW6RjSNs8Zp6pL8G4OA":{"id":"kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.rCxHW6RjSNs8Zp6pL8G4OA","__typename":"Work","legacyId":13946897,"bestBook":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.fEaYCkLkHcRBmFuGZhIe2A"},"details":{"__typename":"WorkDetails","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/13946897-here-home-hope","shelvesUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/shelves/13946897-here-home-hope","publicationTime":1304233200000,"originalTitle":"","awardsWon":[{"__typename":"Award","name":"Writer's Digest Self-Published Book Competition","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/award/show/8019-writer-s-digest-self-published-book-competition","awardedAt":1293868800000,"category":"Mainsteam/Literary Fiction","hasWon":false},{"__typename":"Award","name":"USA Best Book Award","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/award/show/9626-usa-best-book-award","awardedAt":1293868800000,"category":"Fiction: Chick Lit/Women's Lit","hasWon":true},{"__typename":"Award","name":"Natio